attributes.additional_details:
I call the Government to;

Make it law to label clearly Halal and Kosher sourced food on packaging, whilst discussing the possibility of imposing fines on those who fail to label their Halal/Kosher food.

People have the right to eat, or avoid foodstuffs with certain properties, ingredients or production methods. This includes meat that has been slaughtered to abide by certain rituals; e.g yet not inclusive to Halal and Kosher meat. Whilst people of the appropriate religions have their right to consume such food, others have the right to not eat it if they don't want to, they have the freedom to choose.
